<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6920> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6920" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 129 (S. C. de Agro Pergameno). In D.-G. 4.323, note 12, it is suggested that this Pompeius was a cousin of the Consul of 89, but if the S. C. de Agro Pergameno is correctly dated in 129 B. C., he was more probably an uncle." .
